@apphost=http://localhost:8080

### Start the PatientIntake workflow
POST {{ apphost }}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P-1042",
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "condition": "bacterial sinusitis",
  "medication": "amoxicillin",
  "dosage": 500
}

### Get the workflow output
GET {{ apphost }}/output
